WEBVTT

00:02.823 --> 00:04.089
Linda is not here right now.

00:04.447 --> 00:05.587
Can I take a message?

00:06.333 --> 00:07.364
This is her husband.

00:07.824 --> 00:09.237
Could you ask her to call me?

00:09.669 --> 00:14.031
I'm at my office, but she needs to call me at extension number 204.

00:15.117 --> 00:16.286
I'd better write this down.

00:16.765 --> 00:18.497
Hold on a moment while I find a pen.

00:19.021 --> 00:20.408
OK. Go ahead.

00:21.298 --> 00:28.031
My office number is 471-3006 extension 204.

00:28.841 --> 00:31.375
Let me repeat that back to make sure I got it.

00:32.185 --> 00:36.881
471-3006 and extension 204.

00:37.621 --> 00:38.343
That's right.

00:38.984 --> 00:42.599
I'll tell her to call you as soon as she gets back to the office.

00:43.230 --> 00:44.442
Thank you very much.

